<BaseLayout
  title="Home"
  description="Welcome to Graphics Programming Virtual Meetup, a weekly virtual meetup dedicated to graphics programming!"
>
  <h1>Graphics Programming Virtual Meetup</h1>

  <p>
    Welcome, Computer Graphics lovers! We are a virtual meetup dedicated to
    graphics programming.
  </p>
  <p>Since 2020, we have hosted hundreds of meetings almost every week.</p>
  <p>
    We usually work through computer graphics books or articles on a weekly
    basis, though sometimes we have project presentations from members.
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>
      Join our weekly
      <a href="https://www.meetup.com/graphics-programming-virtual-meetup">
        meetings
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>Join our <a href="https://discord.gg/TsTDb4uYfR">Discord group</a></li>
    <li>
      See our
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbX05PBAE-582PYaRXdjRnw">
        Youtube channel
      </a>
      for past video recording
    </li>
    <li>
      Follow us on
      <a href="https://mastodon.gamedev.place/@graphicsmeetup" rel="me">
        Mastodon
      </a>
      and
      <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/gpvm.bsky.social">Bluesky</a>
    </li>
  </ul>

